== 其他资产 ==
=== 互联网 ===
通过派拉蒙媒體網絡，将其拥有的互联网资产转由其运营，例如：{{Link-en|MTV新闻|MTV News}}和{{Link-en|绝妙电视|AwesomenessTV}}。维亚康姆CBS国内传媒网还曾在2000年代后期运营过一个[[虚拟世界|虚拟世界]]系统——虚拟MTV（{{lang|en|Virtual MTV}}）<ref>{{cite news |last=Seiler |first=Joey |url=http://www.engagedigital.com/blog/2009/02/05/virtual-mtv-launches-alpha-of-browserbased-experience/ |title=Virtual MTV Launches Alpha of Browser-Based Experience |work=Engage Digital Media |date=2009-02-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110509074324/http://www.engagedigital.com/blog/2009/02/05/virtual-mtv-launches-alpha-of-browserbased-experience/ |archivedate=2011-05-09 |accessdate=2020-05-23 }}</ref>。除此之外，它还曾拥有[[尼奥宠物|尼奥宠物]]、{{Link-en|原子娱乐|Atom Entertainment}}、{{Link-en|点评教授网|RateMyProfessors.com}}等网站，但都在2000年代和2010年代关闭或出售给其他公司。

=== 电子游戏 ===
2006年，维亚康姆集团以1.75亿美元收购了{{Link-en|Harmonix|Harmonix}}，这是一家专注[[音乐游戏|音乐游戏]]的电子游戏工作室，同时它也是《{{Link-en|吉他英雄|Guitar Hero}}》的最初开发商<ref>{{cite web |author1=Matt Martin |title=MTV acquires Harmonix for USD $175 million |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/mtv-acquires-harmonix-for-usd-175-million |publisher=GamesIndustry |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116040139/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/mtv-acquires-harmonix-for-usd-175-million |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，这家公司便推出了《{{Link-en|摇滚乐队 (电子游戏)|Rock Band (video game)|摇滚乐队}}》系列游戏。同年，维亚康姆还收购了面向游戏的通讯平台{{Link-en|Xfire|Xfire}}<ref>{{cite web |author1=Gamespot Staff |title=Viacom to acquire Xfire |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/viacom-to-acquire-xfire/1100-6148208/ |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804052818/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/viacom-to-acquire-xfire/1100-6148208/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年，Harmonix被单独剥离出售给一家投资公司，从此成为一家独立的游戏工作室<ref>{{cite web |author1=Josh Halliday |title=Viacom sells Rock Band game studio |url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2010/dec/24/rock-band-developer-sold-by-viacom |publisher=[[卫报|卫报]] |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804051120/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2010/dec/24/rock-band-developer-sold-by-viacom |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Meagan Marie |title=Viacom Sells Harmonix To Columbus Nova |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/12/23/-viacom-sells-harmonix-to-columbus-nova.aspx |publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2019-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826114118/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/12/23/-viacom-sells-harmonix-to-columbus-nova.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年被出售的还有{{lang|en|Xfire}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Exclusive: Titan Gaming Takes Xfire Off Viacom's Hands |url=https://techcrunch.com/2010/08/02/exclusive-titan-gaming-takes-xfire-off-viacoms-hands/ |website=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |publisher=Verizon Media |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2020-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608083943/https://techcrunch.com/2010/08/02/exclusive-titan-gaming-takes-xfire-off-viacoms-hands/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年，维亚康姆成立了一家内部游戏公司——345游戏（{{lang|en|345 Games}}），这家公司主要致力于开发基于喜剧中心和音乐电视网属性的游戏<ref>{{cite web |author1=Philiana Ng |title=MTV Networks Group Launches 345 Games |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mtv-networks-group-launches-345-176160 |publisher=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809151040/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mtv-networks-group-launches-345-176160 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 国际事业 ==
{{Main2|{{Link-en|派拉蒙國際電視網|Paramount International Networks}}}}

{{Link-en|派拉蒙國際電視網|Paramount International Networks}}是派拉蒙媒體網絡的下属事业部门，其总部分别位于[[纽约|纽约]]、[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[华沙|华沙]]和[[布宜诺斯艾利斯|布宜诺斯艾利斯]]等地。该事业部门由[[音乐电视网|MTV]]、[[尼克儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]]、[[喜剧中心|喜剧中心]]、[[VH1|流行电视第一台]]和{{Link-en|Colors|Colors TV}}等组成。

派拉蒙國際電視網由以下电视网络组成：
* {{Link-en|派拉蒙欧亚非電視網|Paramount Networks EMEAA}}
** 派拉蒙北欧電視網
** 派拉蒙南欧、中东及非洲電視網
* 派拉蒙亚太電視網
** {{Link-en|十号电视网控股|Ten Network Holdings}}
** {{Link-en|维亚康姆18|Viacom 18}}
* {{Link-en|派拉蒙美洲電視網|Paramount Networks Americas}}<ref>{{cite web |title=MTV Latin America Confirms Rock Band Thirty Seconds to Mars to Perform at MTV World Stage Mexico |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mtv-latin-america-confirms-rock-band-thirty-seconds-to-mars-to-perform-at-mtv-world-stage-mexico-98605484.html |publisher=[[美通社|美通社]] |accessdate=2020-05-23 |archive-date=2018-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210123908/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mtv-latin-america-confirms-rock-band-thirty-seconds-to-mars-to-perform-at-mtv-world-stage-mexico-98605484.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

派拉蒙國際電視網網此前的旗下品牌还包括{{Link-en|TMF (电视频道)|The Music Factory|TMF}}和{{Link-en|VIVA音乐频道|VIVA (German TV channel)}}，以及[[Nitrome|Nitrome]]、震荡波（{{lang|en|Shockwave}}）、瘾游戏（{{lang|en|Addicting Games}}）、{{Link-en|Atom.com|Atom.com}}和{{Link-en|Xfire|Xfire}}等数字资产。目前这些资产或被合并，或被关停及出售。

